  6,63,"Say, ňĻO Prophet,ňļ ‚ÄúWho rescues you from the darkest times on land and at sea? He ňĻaloneňļ you call upon with humility, openly and secretly: ‚ÄúIf You rescue us from this, we will be ever grateful.‚ÄĚ"
