  6,65,"Say, ‚ÄúHe ňĻaloneňļ has the power to unleash upon you a torment from above or below you or split you into ňĻconflictingňļ factions and make you taste the violence of one another.‚ÄĚ See how We vary the signs, so perhaps they will comprehend"
